  "title": "Counter Clerk (Container Depot / West)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Update and track container movements.</li>\n  <li>Perform data entry and maintain an organized filing system.</li>\n  <li>Collect cash payments and issue receipts.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with external parties regarding container release and collection.</li>\n  <li>Communicate internally to ensure seamless operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
